  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/14290/" target="_blank">【人文与社会】译丛——译林出版社</a>
                <span class="pl">(彼岸)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/84216/" target="_blank">我的书单（政治学理论）</a>
                <span class="pl">(午夜书生)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/139259/" target="_blank">空间诗学</a>
                <span class="pl">(歌尔德蒙)</span>
